# Deployment Owner

The deployment owner username is **Reave** (override per install with `ADMIN_USERNAME`).

Owner-only UI today:
- **Plugins** page (account menu → Plugins)
- `GET` / `PUT` `/api/admin/features`

Match is case-insensitive against the Clerk user's `username`, `firstName`, or full name.

Other signed-in users can use the rest of admin; they do not see Plugins or manage feature toggles.
